Based out of Pune. It shares great similarities with Krakow.
Live with my beautiful wife and a lovely daughter.
I love writing poems, give them tone and rhythm, and sing.
I am a nature lover and a gadget freak at the same time.
Fond of good food (veg) and beers.
I love driving to, exploring, and indulging in new cities and their culture.
